      Fields in org.sakaiproject.content.api declared as GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode.GROUPED
      grouped access; only members of the getGroup() groups (authorization groups) have access
      static GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode.INHERITED
      inherited access; must look up a hierarchy to determine actual access
      static GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode.SITE
      channel (site) level access to the entity

      Access the access mode defined locally for the entity.
      GroupAwareEntity.AccessMode GroupAwareEntity.getInheritedAccess()
      Access the actual access mode used to compute who has access to the entity (usually SITE or GROUPED, but not INHERITED).
